          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " is a separate, purely-computational module for the live interaction surface around making and re-pointing connections — it is not the routing algorithm itself, but the logic that decides where a connector endpoint should snap while a person is dragging it. It ports two pieces from BlockSuite's "
